                                <condition>The ogham inscription is incomplete. The first section of the ogham inscription is clearly legible, except for two letters which are missing. The end portion of the inscription is now broken off. The stone was already broken when found. It was extensively fractured and subsequent exposure to weathering led to its disintegration and loss of part of the inscription that had previously been read. It was subsequently reassembled and reconstructed where necessary in accordance with Rev. Grant's early reading (Kermode 1907, 96).</condition>
